    "This evolution is depicted in Fig. 19.",
    "The Y-axis displays the number of cases per variable, which, for readability in Fig. 19, has been divided into three areas, analysing the evolution of the type of iVR experience, HMD type, and type of interaction.",
    "The X-axis shows the temporal evolution, divided into three triennia to facilitate the analysis and the conclusions: Triennium 1 (2013-2016), Triennium 2 (2017-2019), and Triennium 3 (2020-2022).",
    "Although Triennium 1 spans a period of 4 years, it effectively covers three years of analysis, as there were no data available for 2014.",
    "These three evolutions were chosen as they were the most technologically relevant among those analysed, clearly demonstrating an evolution."
